{"tid":1642270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"的士佬撞人過程拆彈","createTime":"2019-10-09T15:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T13:39:19.000Z","uid":198899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32c1d330548cea1e1ccf29fdef1c83a8e494fed5","tid":1642270,"uid":198899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191007/s00001/1570386979555/%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%BD%AE%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B73%E4%BA%BA-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%AD%E3%80%8C%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191007%2Fs00001%2F1570386979555%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%2582%25B73%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586%25E3%2580%258D&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=3be01a1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191007%2Fs00001%2F1570386979555%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%2592%259E%25E5%2582%25B73%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586%25E3%2580%258D&h=83dfcc26\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191007/s00001/1570386979555/%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%BD%AE%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B73%E4%BA%BA-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%AD%E3%80%8C%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<blockquote>昨午約5時，有傳媒拍攝到一輛的士於深水埗南昌街高速行駛，當時路上有小量示威者遊行。網上片段所見，5時許同一車牌號碼之的士抵達欽州街近長沙灣道路口長沙灣政府合署對開時，疑因有示威者經過時拍打的士，的士司機突然急速轉彎剷上行人路並撞向人群。<br />\n<br />\n多名示威者隨即包圍的士，並將的士司機拉出車廂圍毆，司機被打至頭破血流及指罵為「殺人犯」，之後多人用身體擋住他，要求其他人停止攻擊。該的士司機的個人物品，包括身分證及信用卡被放在胸前，其後現場有急救員為其急救。</blockquote><br />\n第一條片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rzj_tXX4YCI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRzj_tXX4YCI&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=1dd59f4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rzj_tXX4YCI</a><br />\n第二條片: <a href=\"https://streamable.com/pi19m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fpi19m&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=141484c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/pi19m</a><br />\n第二個post既描述: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1633224/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1633224/page/1</a><br />\n首先明報確定咗一開始喺深水埗南昌街出現既嗰架的士同後尾撞人既喺同一架，第一條片見到好彩冇乜人喺路上面如果唔喺就一定出事，架的士根本就喺加速要撞到人。<br />\n但宜家班藍一直喺度focus喺第二條片，講緊話喺手足獅鳥導致交通意外...但依然啲片都仲唔夠充分，但個的士司機一定唔喺無辜。<br />\n推爆佢ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14dc9d963ed0ad0ede5c9c99e6907e87c635da2","tid":1642270,"uid":198899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuBOU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuBOU3.jpg&h=35486de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvaYhOo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvaYhOo.jpg&h=6b91bbb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zVQTmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zVQTmK.jpg&h=9cff4d11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b14ebf34969cacf019d308ec6dbf1777cb0852f8","tid":1642270,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:57:45.000Z","msg":"放心我相信手足"},{"pid":"2a188e07d2c54c7e98ab9a16ccf8d39733d568c3","tid":1642270,"uid":198899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"依家個的士司機上埋電視大叫無辜啦點解冇人理？？？？"}]}